title: You've found your new home in the heart of Boca Raton!
posting_body: ['Come live the Boca lifestyle!', 'Magnificent end unit makes this model the most attractive in Pineapple Walk!', 'Enjoy a beautiful, open floor plan and stunning finishes in this two-story, two-bedroom townhouse.', 'Beautifully landscaped grounds include a community pool and sitting area.', 'Tastefully upgraded finishes include new waterproof vinyl flooring upstairs, 5-inch baseboards in both bedrooms, walk in closets, stainless steel appliances, washer, dryer and more.', 'Enjoy walking out your front door to find shopping, dining and entertainment just steps away with the plaza right across the street!', 'only 1.9 miles away from Town Center at Boca Raton and 10 minutes away from Mizner Park!', 'Located near A rated schools.', "You've found your new home in the heart of Boca Raton!", 'Contact us to schedule a tour today.', 'Please TEXT me your NAME and', 'AD REFERENCE', 'below and We will contact you ASAP.', 'Book your appointment online today!', 'ANNUAL RENTALS ONLY.', 'Ad Reference:', 'F-10335772', 'Text at:', 'show contact info', 'Ask for ANDREW', 'Availability can change daily, If this rental is not available or isn’t the property for you, Text me or call me and We will help you find the right residence for you.', 'We have rentals all over Palm Beach and Broward County!']
